statement error
ATTACH 'test.db' AS test (TYPE sqlite);
----
db error: ERROR: LOAD is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be loaded at runtime.
If you need the "sqlite_scanner" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.
